name: "BLACK ON BLACK" CLASSIC
description:
Introducing our "Black on Black Classic" Jeremy Lin black tee.

Our design showcases our favorite players team and number, as well as one of his favorite bible verses. 

Shirt made in the USA 

by American Apparel:

An ultra-soft, ultra-comfy unisex T-shirt that feels like you’ve owned it for years the moment you put it on, and for years to come.

Poly-Cotton (50% Polyester / 50% Cotton) construction (Heather Grey contains 10% Polyester)

Durable rib neckband

Fits slimmer than their 2001
